    <body>
      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="X06ACWJS">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-X06ACWJS-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X06ACWJS-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X06ACWJS-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">Merry Dan, as tis fitting&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-X06ACWJS-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X06ACWJS-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X06ACWJS-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1">To Sheridan sendeth greeting.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-X06ACWJS-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X06ACWJS-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X06ACWJS-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-1" n="1">|Obsignatam mitto gratam</l>
            <l rend="indent(3)" xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-2" n="2">||Veniam Sheridan</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-3" n="3">|Quia dixisti Vultu tristi</l>
            <l rend="indent(3)" xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-4" n="4">||Peto a Te Mi Dan.</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-5" n="5"><lb/>|Pacemque præsto nec Molesto</l>
            <l rend="indent(3)" xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-6" n="6">||Omnino in præsenti</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-7" n="7">|Ut sis totus meus devotus</l>
            <l rend="indent(3)" xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-8" n="8">||Corpore et Menti.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-9" n="9"><lb/>The Suit which humbly You have made</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-10" n="10">Is fully and Maturely weigh'd;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-11" n="11">«LD»And as 'tis Your Petition:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-12" n="12">I do Forgive for well I know</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-13" n="13">Since You're so Bruis'd another Blow</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-14" n="14">«LD»Wou'd Break the Head of Priscian.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-15" n="15">'Tis not my Purpose or Intent</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-16" n="16">That You shou'd suffer Banishment,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-17" n="17">«LD»I Pardon, now You've Courted</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-18" n="18">And Yet I fear this Clemency</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-19" n="19">Will come too late to profit thee</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-20" n="20">«LD»For You're with Grief Transported.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-21" n="21">However this I do Command</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-22" n="22">That You Your Birch do take in hand</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-23" n="23">«LD»Read Concord and Syntax-on;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-24" n="24">The Bays You own are onely Mine</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-25" n="25">Do You then still Your Nouns Decline</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-26" n="26">«LD»Since You've declin'd────</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-27" n="27">«LD»Dan: Jackson.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X06ACWJS-line-28" n="28"><lb/>I think you should have signed your Petition, but that may be done, when I see you next. However I keep the Original under your own Hand, and send you inclosed only the Copy.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
